title: Ep. 491 - A Sorry Solves Everything - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The last option now remains is to break the door and get inside. Sodhi decides to do the deed. He finally breaks in with all his power. Entering the house finds Daya asleep as she had some cough syrup. Jethalal wakes her up and apologizes.

title: Ep. 492 - Tapu Sena Is Confused - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu Sena is enjoying their vacation and while playing cricket, hey cause a fight between Iyer and Jethalal. Tapu Sena goes to Taarak to ask for his advice as they are confused as to what to do in their vacations.

title: Ep. 493 - Magic Show In Gokuldham - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu Sena informs Bhide about the magic show organized by Taarak. Tapu Sena and all the society members are excited about the magic show. Later, the famous magician Munnalal arrives at Gokuldham for the magic show.

title: Ep. 494 - Magi Show Is A Success - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The magician starts showing his talent and all the society members enjoy it. The magician also performs different magic by involving the society members.

title: Ep. 495 - Tapu Sena Wants To Learn Magic - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The magic show continues and the ladies and Tapu Sena also involved in the magic. Tapu Sena expresses their wish o learn magic from Munnalal and the parents also give permission for it.

title: Ep. 496 - Tapu Sena Performs Magic - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu Sena goes to Munnalal to larn magic and he also teaches them the tricks involved in magic. Tapu Sena shows the magic learned from Munnalal to the society members and everybody is shocked to see it.

title: Ep. 497 - Police For Tapu Sena - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: In the process of showing magic to everybody, Tapu Sena by mistake misplaces Madhavi's money and she becomes mad at them. Bhide makes a big fight in the society regarding the money. The society members search for money everywhere in society.

title: Ep. 498 - Dr. Hathi In Gokuldham - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethalal accuses Taarak and makes him the reason for Tapu Sena's mistake. Tapu is scared of the police and begs his parents that he will not repeat the mistake. Dr. Hathi returns from the Naturo Camp and they tell that they couldn't reduce the weight

title: Ep. 499 - Champaklal Disciplines Jethalal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Champaklal is sick. Jethalal gets him the medicine. Champaklal makes sure that Jethalal takes care of his health and drinks warm water only. He also tells him not to eat street food and only eat a homecooked meal.

title: Ep. 500 - Tapu Sena Make A Scene - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu ruins Bhide's Balcony with his mud shots. Furious Bhide goes down to teach Tapu a lesson. Tapu bites Bhide and causes a scene. Jethalal defends Tapu and argues with Bhide.

title: Ep. 501 - The Society Fund - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide conducts a meeting and informs everyone about the cost of the new paint quotation. Bhide tells that they do not have enough money in the society funds to support the painting.

title: Ep. 502 - Daya Is Mesmerized - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: All the ladies go shopping with Babita and after coming home, Daya is mesmerized by the concept of a credit card. Babita tries explaining to all the ladies how a credit card works.

title: Ep. 503 - Ordering Credit Cards - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya and her housewife friends are just too fascinated with the concept of credit cards and decide to order it for them. Bank sends a person and he tells them that he has faith in them.

title: Ep. 504 - The Bill - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: After the women get their credit cards, they go shopping. Everyone shops till their heart are content. Only when they receive a bill, they understand that the man was a fraud.

title: Ep. 505 - The Bad People  - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: After they refuse to pay the money, the bank person threatens to send people to hurt their husbands or their kids. The men in the society are worried as well.
